    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create your own Bloodline</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You decide the fate of your nobles. Each noble has their own genes resulting in different stats, traits, and appearance inherited from their parents. Match your characters with other houses to create the next generation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Matchmaker </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as one of the four houses and match your lords and ladies with the other houses. Each house has distinct starting genes with strengths and weaknesses.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Monarch</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the ranks of nobility and make your family prosper. Claim more titles by winning tourneys, making tactical marriages, or snagging them away from another successor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152570/extras/fce550550aa247709b5ed6947b36eef5.poster.avif?t=1772222318\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152570/extras/fce550550aa247709b5ed6947b36eef5.webm?t=1772222318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152570/extras/fce550550aa247709b5ed6947b36eef5.mp4?t=1772222318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
